      <title>TikTok creators go from sadness and fear to...'whatever!' over app's future</title>
      <author>Chloe Veltman</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/04/05/nx-s1-5351788/sale-trump-tiktok-china-creators-fatigue</link>
