      <title>'Your RIF notice is not cancelled.' Inside a chaotic week of massive layoffs at HHS</title>
      <author>Rob Stein</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2025/04/05/g-s1-58312/hhs-layoffs-rif-cdc-fda-nih</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2025/04/05/g-s1-58312/hhs-layoffs-rif-cdc-fda-nih</comments>
